condition.narrative: The Borrower, through the MOLSP, shall, not later than December 30, 2007, have the physical outputs and functional results underPart A of the Project audited for at least 30% of the local SWO.

title.narrative: Standard office model is developed, piloted, evaluated and formally approved

comment.narrative: 99% of the LWOs are using the Standard office model approved back in 2007.

title.narrative: Annual Social reports prepared, published and disseminated in 2007, 2008, 2009 and 2010

comment.narrative: All 4 Social reports have been released

title.narrative: # of oblast social welfare offices capable of carrying out analyses and monitoring of the benefit payments.

comment.narrative: Not yet achieved; in progress. The underlying MIS software is in operational acceptance testing in Vinnytska oblast. The resultwill be only achieved after MIS has been rolled out in all oblasts.

title.narrative: Functional review of DSDS completed and business plan prepared in 2006

target.value: Two rounds of project impact evaluation—baseline in 2008 and follow-up in 2009

title.narrative: # of rayon/city welfare offices implemented new "single window" service model

comment.narrative: Initially, 754; since project approval in 2005, the number of the LWOs has increased to 756.

title.narrative: Increase in number of benefits that are processed per month per staff of local welfare office
Reduction in time for client in-take in local welfare office
Increase in percentage of social assistance cash benefits received by poor families

comment.narrative: This is the assessment of targeting accuracy of cash benefits in Ukraine in 2011 that is assessed on full set of 2011 HBS data.

title.narrative: % of population aware of eligibility criteria for social assistance benefits.

comment.narrative: The 2009 number used in the last ISR is updated based on 2010 project impact evaluation

title.narrative: Evaluation of social assistance programs completed
Public information and education strategy developed and approved in 2006

comment.narrative: The strategy has been developed and approved at the beginning of 2011

title.narrative: Social Development Database improved (monitoring indicators etc)

comment.narrative: Social Development Database will improve even further after MIS national roll-out in completed in 2012
